column2: SELECT m.id, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,   p.objid AS sdssid, p.ra AS ra2, p.dec AS dec2,    n.distance,    p.g, p.r, p.PetroRad_g AS radiusg, p.PetroRad_r as radiusr into mydb.output_table from MyDB.Void_Dwarfs AS m   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.RA, m.DEC, #) AS n   JOIN photoObj AS p ON p.objid = n.objid   JOIN specObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid    AND s.Class = &&&    AND s.z <= #
